                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7882" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0811</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1450 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">果香四溢：洪九果品织 “ 数 ” 网，“ 链 ” 出品牌智慧果</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Fruit Fragrance: Hongjiu Fruit weaves &quot;digital&quot; network, &quot;chain&quot; out of branded fruits of wisdom</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">冯益，王璐瑶，张海涛，熊国保</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东华理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆洪九果品股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商业模式创新；“端到端”供应链；全产业链运营；数字化管理系统“洪九星桥”；多元鲜果品牌组合</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Business model innovation; &quot;end-to-end&quot; supply chain; whole industry chain operation; digital management system &quot;Hongjiu Xingqiao&quot;; Diversified portfolio of fresh fruit brands</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鲜果行业存在着标准化程度低、数字化水平弱、品牌化建设难的果业“魔咒”，诸多鲜果分销企业陷入产品损耗大、运行效率低、创利盈收差的“迷雾”。本案例描述了洪九果品通过“端到端”供应链构建壁垒、全产业链运营高效协同、数字化管理系统驱动赋能、鲜果多元品牌塑造差异，逐一击破行业痛点，破解发展“魔咒”，驱散“眼”前“迷雾”，引领鲜果行业转型升级。本案例以洪九果品的发展历程为主线，旨在引导学员深入思考鲜果市场消费需求提档升级和鲜果产业迎来迭代升级背景下潜在的企业发展机会，促使学习者深刻理解驱动商业模式创新的内外因素，掌握商业模式创新的路径，并进一步引导学员探寻各分销企业如何紧跟行业发展“步伐”，实现可持续发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The fresh fruit industry has a &quot;curse&quot; of low standardization,weak digitization,and difficulty in brand building.Many fresh fruit distribution enterprises are trapped in a &quot;fog&quot; of high product loss,low operating efficiency,and poor profit and loss.This case describes Hong Jiu Fruit&#39;s efforts to build barriers in the &quot;end-to-end&quot; supply chain,achieve efficient collaboration in the entire industry chain operation,drive empowerment through digital management systems,and create diverse brand differentiation for fresh fruits,breaking through industry pain points one by one, breaking the &quot;curse&quot; of development,dispelling the &quot;fog&quot; in front of the &quot;eyes&quot;,and leading the transformation and upgrading of the fresh fruit industry.This case takes the development process of Hongjiu Fruit as the main thread,aiming to guide students to deeply consider the potential development opportunities of enterprises in the context of upgrading the consumption demand of the fresh fruit market and the iterative upgrading of the fresh fruit industry.It encourages learners to deeply understand the internal and external factors driving business model innovation,grasp the path of business model innovation,and further guide students to explore how distribution enterprises can keep up with the industry&#39;s development &quot;pace&quot;,to achieve sustainable development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新与创业管理》、《商业模式》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商业模式创新的驱动因素；商业模式创新的路径；商业模式画布理论；价值创造路径</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
